<noinclude>
Per-user expense / income summary, driven by Cargo queries against the
<code>Expenses</code> and <code>Income</code> tables. Pass the username
as the first parameter (or default to the current page name, so adding
<code><nowiki>{{User receipts}}</nowiki></code> to a User: page works
without an argument).

Usage on a user page:
<pre>{{User receipts}}</pre>

Usage anywhere:
<pre>{{User receipts|UserName}}</pre>

This template is intended to be placed on a User: page; if you install
[https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:CreateUserPage CreateUserPage]
you can have it auto-added when a user is registered. See
[[Help:Receipts]].

When the query has zero matches, Cargo's <code>default=</code> kicks in
with a short prose note (rendered instead of the table — Cargo skips
the inline <code>intro=</code> / <code>outro=</code> wrappers when
there are no rows). When there are results, the inline intro / outro
plus the rows are all parsed together as a single HTML table — note
the table tags are inline, not sub-templates, because Cargo's
<code>format=template</code> only honors the literal <code>intro=</code>
and <code>outro=</code> params (not <code>intro template=</code>).

[[Category:Receipt templates]]
</noinclude><includeonly><templatestyles src="Template:User receipts/styles.css" />
=== Expenses ===
{{#cargo_query:tables=Expenses
|fields=_pageName=page,date,payee,total,currency,category
|where=assignee="{{#if:{{{1|}}}|{{{1}}}|{{ROOTPAGENAME}}}}"
|order by=date DESC
|limit=20
|format=template
|template=User receipts row expense
|intro=<table class="wikitable sortable rs-ledger-table" style="width:100%"><tr><th>Date</th><th>Payee</th><th style="text-align:right">Total</th><th>Category</th><th class="unsortable" style="width:3em;text-align:center">Link</th></tr>
|outro=</table>
|named args=yes
|default=''No expenses for this user.''
}}

[{{fullurl:Special:Ledger|kind=expense&range=all&assignee={{urlencode:{{#if:{{{1|}}}|{{{1}}}|{{ROOTPAGENAME}}}}}}}} View all expenses in the ledger →]

=== Income ===
{{#cargo_query:tables=Income
|fields=_pageName=page,date,payer,total,currency,category
|where=assignee="{{#if:{{{1|}}}|{{{1}}}|{{ROOTPAGENAME}}}}"
|order by=date DESC
|limit=20
|format=template
|template=User receipts row income
|intro=<table class="wikitable sortable rs-ledger-table" style="width:100%"><tr><th>Date</th><th>Payer</th><th style="text-align:right">Total</th><th>Category</th><th class="unsortable" style="width:3em;text-align:center">Link</th></tr>
|outro=</table>
|named args=yes
|default=''No income for this user.''
}}

[{{fullurl:Special:Ledger|kind=income&range=all&assignee={{urlencode:{{#if:{{{1|}}}|{{{1}}}|{{ROOTPAGENAME}}}}}}}} View all income in the ledger →]
</includeonly>
